PEOPLE
v.
LOPEZ S228372 Supreme Court of California. OCTOBER 31, 2018 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

Dismissed and remanded to CA 6. Review in the above-captioned matter is dismissed in light of this court's decision in People v. DeHoyos (2018) 4 Cal.5th 594, 229 Cal.Rptr.3d 687, 412 P.3d 368. ( Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(b).) Corrigan, J., was absent and did not participate.
